import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './Main.css'; function Main() { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ CustName: '', ShortName: '', CustType: '', Phone: '', Fax: '', email: '', URL: '', Address: '', City: '', State: '', Zip: '', Taxable: false, SalTaxId: '', ShpAddress: '', ShpCity: '', ShpState: '', ShpZip: '', Balance: '', CreditAmount: '', LastInvoice: '', LastSaleDate: '', PayTerms: '', SalesRep: '', LastModDate: '', LastModuser: '' }); const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value, type, checked } = e.target; setFormData({ ...formData, [name]: type === 'checkbox' ? checked : value }); }; const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Handle form submission, for example, sending the data to an API endpoint const response = await fetch('/api/save-customer', { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify(formData) }); if (response.ok) { alert('Customer details saved successfully!'); } else { alert('Failed to save customer details.'); } }; return (

























); }; export default Main;
